View Harmful Content Notification in a Prompt Response

Quickly identify harmful language in prompt responses for safer, inclusive interactions.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.
When: The notification is available on a rolling basis starting in sandbox environments on July 9, 2024 and in production on July 11, 2024.
How: Craft, save, and preview your prompt. If any harmful content is in the prompt response, a Harmful Content badge is shown above the prompt response.
title: Harmful Content Detection in Salesforce
